 based on your experience, skills and passion. When you signify interest in the Project, please tell us the pronouns you use and any reasonable adjustments you may need during the contractor-accreditation interview process.\n\nPlease note that contractor-accreditation meetings are conducted virtually.\n\nWe celebrate all types of skills and backgrounds at Canva so even if you don’t feel like your skills quite match what’s listed above - we still want to hear from you!\n\nCheck out lifeatcanva.com for more info.\n\n#LI-Remote"}
